- OS Version: CentOS7

Steps to Reproduce:

1. Set up a .NET core project and install extension
2. Build the project
3. Try to debug it; you will get this error

![selection_001](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/28019043/25404798/3d5fe24e-29cf-11e7-8ff7-89d67f8e97c7.png)

